  "body": "Index.yaml currently requires all of the source URLs to be full URLs. When sources are hosted locally on the same webserver, it should be possible to just specify a relative URL. For example\r\n```\r\nurls\r\n- chart-0.0.0.tgz\r\n```\r\nwould imply\r\n```\r\nurls\r\n- http://repository/path/containing/index/chart-0.0.0.tgz\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis would make much more sense than having a relative path cause helm to look under the local filesystem, as it does now.",
